Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:01.60,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}那時候的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:05.34,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}對著無法起飛的螺旋槳做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.80,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}朝著天空的另一半抬頭望去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:12.91,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}光著腳丫肆意奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:17.35,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們永遠都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:24.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}無論誤會與否 就是對生活充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:37.79,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}如同把重要的寶物 藏起來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:46.39,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}再也無法發現那顆深藏起來的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:49.39,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}咕嚕咕嚕轉上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.50,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}用這根魔法之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:58.53,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}把眼淚和晴天混合起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:02.24,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}怕寂寞的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}夢想一定會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:13.77,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們要永遠在一起哦
